[32m│[0m This reveals important information about the filter logic:                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Key Observations:                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. **All payloads blocked identically** - The `<&#115;cript>` bypass is      [32m│[0m
